    <line>Who fillest with thy soul this world of woe</line>
    <line>To whom all things of Earth &amp; Heaven do bow</line>
    <line>In fear &amp; worship-- all-prevailing foe!</line>
    <line rend="indent1">I curse thee! let a sufferer's curse</line>
    <line rend="indent1">Clasp thee, his torturer, like remorse,</line>
    <line rend="indent1">'Till thine Infinity shall be</line>
    <line rend="indent1">A robe of envenomed agony</line>
    <line>And thine Omnipotence a crown of pain</line>
